body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting CarFix. My name is Edward Wood and I will be assisting you today. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Linda. How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling nervous about some recent customer service interactions.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand, Linda. To better assist you, could you please provide me with your phone number, spelled out digit by digit?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's five five five, two five five, four seven eight nine.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you. Could you also provide me with your email address, spelled out character by character?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, it's L-i-n-d-a dot G-o-n-z-a-l-e-z at g-m-a-i-l dot c-o-m.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for sharing that information, Linda. We will address your concerns promptly. I appreciate your time today.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for contacting CarFix. Have a great day, Linda.
